    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      551.08,
      538.34,
      592.03
    ],
    "text": "Fairly heavy showers above 50 mm can be expected at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa and Central provinces and in the Galle and Matara districts.",
